OL,3,CMum's 'nightmare' over hiker missing
OL,4,Cfor six days in Italian Alps
OL,6,FThe mother of a hiker from Hull who
OL,7,Fhas gone missing in the Italian Alps
OL,8,Fsays she is "living someone else's
OL,9,Fnightmare".
OL,11,FMatthew Hall, 33, was last seen
OL,12,Fleaving his accommodation in Chiavenna
OL,13,Fon Tuesday 9 July and sent a
OL,14,Fphotograph to a friend from a mountain
OL,15,Fabove the town that afternoon.
OL,17,FHe was due to fly home to the UK on
OL,18,FSaturday but has not returned.
