OL,3,CMum's 'nightmare' over hiker missing
OL,4,Cfor six days in Italian Alps
OL,6,FHis mother Sara Foster, 62, told the
OL,7,FHull Live website: "I feel like I'm
OL,8,Fliving someone else's nightmare, but
OL,9,FI've just been blown sideways by all
OL,10,Fof his friends. I didn't know them all
OL,11,Fbut I do now.
OL,13,F"The way that they have just leapt
OL,14,Finto action has been unbelievable, it
OL,15,Freally has. I obviously realise that
OL,16,Fhe's very loved. I got a message from
OL,17,Fthe search team this morning ` there
OL,18,Fare apparently five teams who are out
OL,19,Flooking for him."
