OL,3,CMum's 'nightmare' over hiker missing
OL,4,Cfor six days in Italian Alps
OL,6,FA group of colleagues from boradband
OL,7,Fcompany Quickline in Hull, where Mr
OL,8,FHall works, have also travelled to
OL,9,FItaly to help with the search.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for the company said:
OL,12,F"We remain in close contact with
OL,13,FMatt's family and are doing all we can
OL,14,Fto support them during this incredibly
OL,15,Fdifficult time.
OL,17,F"Our thoughts are with Matt and his
OL,18,Floved ones, and we are all hoping for
OL,19,Fa safe and positive outcome."
