OL,3,CMum's 'nightmare' over hiker missing
OL,4,Cfor six days in Italian Alps
OL,6,FMr Hall is 5ft 6ins tall and athletic
OL,7,Fwith curly brown hair. He was wearing
OL,8,Fa beige T-shirt and carrying a black
OL,9,Fbackpack on the day he was last seen.
OL,11,FHe had been staying at B&B Ploncher in
OL,12,FChiavenna.
OL,14,FPolice in Italy believe he may have
OL,15,Fheaded toward Savogno or Dasile from
OL,16,FBorgonuovo, or toward Pianazzola,
OL,17,FDaloo, or Lagunch from Chiavenna.
